Privacy Policy for **ONE DIRECTION LYRICS APP**

Last updated: 30/08/2024

Thank you for choosing ONE DIRECTION LYRICS APP. This privacy policy explains how we handle your information when you use our app. Since ONE DIRECTION LYRICS APP does not collect, store, or share any personal data, we take your privacy very seriously.

1. Information We Do Not Collect
Personal Information: We do not collect any personal information, such as your name, email address, phone number, or contact details.
Usage Data: We do not collect any information related to your usage of the app.
Location Data: We do not track your location or access location data.
Cookies and Tracking Technologies: We do not use cookies or similar technologies to track your activities.
2. No Data Sharing or Selling
Since we do not collect any data, we do not share, sell, or disclose any information to third parties.

3. Third-Party Services
Our app does not use or integrate any third-party services that would collect or share data about you.

4. Children's Privacy
Our app is safe for use by all age groups. As we do not collect any data, we do not knowingly collect any information from children under the age of 13.

5. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page. You are encouraged to review this policy periodically for any updates.

6. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy, please contact us at:

